test_zero_range:
assert [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, ...] == []
  Left contains 8 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8]
test_large_range:
assert [0] == [2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, ...]
  At index 0 diff: 0 != 2
  Right contains 6 more items, first extra item: 3
  Full diff:
  - [2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8]
  + [0]
test_even_range:
assert [0, 1, 3, 5, 7] == [4, 6, 8, 10, 12, 14, ...]
  At index 0 diff: 0 != 4
  Right contains 2 more items, first extra item: 14
  Full diff:
  - [4, 6, 8, 10, 12, 14, 16]
  + [0, 1, 3, 5, 7]
